# .cursor/rules for Project Chimera

## Project Context
This is Project Chimera, an autonomous influencer system.

## Prime Directive
NEVER generate code without checking specs/ first.

## Traceability
Explain your plan before writing code. Log all actions via MCP Sense.

## Additional Rules
- Separate Skills (runtime) from Tools (dev/MCP).
- Commit early, commit often.
- All code must be spec-aligned and test-driven.
